oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Multiple Metal Photoplate Proofs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Brown, Jim Ed; Russell, Johnny; Wagoner, Porter; Jean, Norma; Dickens, Little Jimmy, 1920-2015;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Five black and white halftone portraits of Jim Ed Brown, Johnny Russell, Porter Wagoner, Norma Jean, and Jimmy Dickens. This is probably the proof for the metal photoplate made from the original photo. To view a poster that features the metal photoplates, see https://cdm17118.contentdm.oclc.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/23597.
